  "description": "Ideogram 4.0 open-weight text-to-image model (9.3B single-stream DiT) run locally in ComfyUI. Best-in-class in-image text rendering and typography. Uses a Qwen3-VL-8B text encoder and the Flux 2 VAE, plus a second 'unconditional' transformer that drives dual-branch CFG (there is no user negative prompt). Authored in natural language. Weights are non-commercial; generated images may be used commercially.",
